MCP Server, AI Toolkit, Scaled Column Auto-Sizing, Date and Time Pivoting, React 19.2 Support

## What's New

AG Grid {% migrationVersion() %} adds important new features - [MCP Server](./mcp-server), [AI Toolkit](./ai-toolkit), [Scaled Column Auto-Sizing](./column-sizing/#auto-size-columns-to-fit-cell-contents), [Date and Time Pivoting](./pivoting-column-groups/#pivoting-by-dates-and-times), [React 19.2 Support](https://www.ag-grid.com/react-data-grid/compatibility/#ag-grid--react-compatibility-chart) as described in the [release post](https://blog.ag-grid.com/whats-new-in-ag-grid-34-3/).
These improvements involve no breaking changes as listed below.

